Wiedemann, 1824. Male in 
<bibRefCitation id="D724D7C52B6F9B90BA5BA186B33CD627" author="Becker, T" journalOrPublisher="Capita Zoologica (Den Haag)" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" pagination="1 - 247" title="Dipterologische Studien: Dolichopodidae der Indo-Australischen Region." volume="1" year="1922">Becker 1922</bibRefCitation>
